name: Sarah Martinez
bio: Sarah specializes in luxury coastal properties with over 15 years of experience in high-end real estate. She has a keen eye for architectural details and helps clients find their dream oceanfront homes.

name: Michael Chen
bio: Michael is an expert in downtown and urban properties, specializing in condos, penthouses, and commercial real estate. His deep knowledge of city development trends helps clients make informed investment decisions.

name: Jennifer Walsh
bio: Jennifer has a passion for historic and heritage properties. She specializes in craftsman homes, Victorian houses, and other architectural gems, helping preserve their character while modernizing for today's lifestyle.

name: David Rodriguez
bio: David focuses on modern urban living spaces including lofts, townhouses, and contemporary homes in trendy neighborhoods. He understands the lifestyle needs of young professionals and growing families.

name: Lisa Thompson
bio: Lisa is a luxury property specialist serving Beverly Hills and surrounding prestigious areas. She has extensive experience with high-net-worth clients and exclusive properties in gated communities.
